# 3. Development Progress

## Core Directory Interface

The main directory layout has been created.

Implemented features include:

* Member photo grid
* Responsive layout
* Desktop grid view
* Single-column mobile layout

Member cards display:

* Photo
* Name
* Ministry (optional)

Clicking a card opens the **member profile view**.

---

## Profile System

Member profiles display detailed information including:

* Member photo
* Name
* Ministry
* Phone number
* Email address
* Address
* Birthday
* Anniversary
* Household
* Last updated date

Profiles include interactive functionality:

Phone numbers:

* Tap to call on mobile devices

Emails:

* Tap to open email client

Addresses:

* Tap to open location in Google Maps

Photos:

* Tap to open fullscreen photo viewer

---

## Household / Family View

A household system has been implemented.

Features:

* Household name appears in member profiles
* Tapping a household shows all family members
* Family page displays circular profile photos
* Clicking a family member opens their profile

Navigation behavior:

* Opening a member from a family page
* Closing that member returns to the **family page**, not the directory

---

## Search System

A search bar has been implemented.

Search behavior includes:

* Real-time filtering while typing
* Prefix matching instead of substring matching

Example behavior:

Typing:

Li

Results include:

Lindsey Johnson
Barry Lightfoot

Results exclude:

Alicia Johnson
Ralph Blighton

Search checks both:

* First names
* Last names

